<h2>Facebook wants to unify the chats of all its social media platforms!</h2>
<p>We are already aware of the fact that Facebook is planning to merge the chat section of all of its social media platforms. This will allow users to seamlessly cross-message among Messenger, Instagram, and WhatsApp. With this new infrastructure, the social media giant wants to allow users who are on any one of the apps to communicate with the remaining ones. Furthermore, this system will be end-to-end encrypted according to CEO Mark Zuckerberg.</p>
